Name:                nettle
Version:             0.1.1
Synopsis:            safe nettle binding
Description:
  safe binding for the nettle (<http://www.lysator.liu.se/~nisse/nettle/nettle.html>) library.
  Tested with nettle-2.7.1, might work with 2.5, does NOT WORK with 3.0.
